title: B and H Dairy Vegetarian Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Eastern European, Kosher, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. B&H Dairy Vegetarian restaurant is all veggie except for fish dishes. A proper old fashioned diner, with a counter and stools as well as tables. Extensive kosher vegetarian menu with Eastern European influence. Stuffed cabbage and blintzes. soups, challah bread, fresh juices. Large portions. Vegans to specify.
